About Gary's Oyster Bar
& Seafood House
We are a friendly little place with a cozy atmosphere and we pride ourselves as a true Florida seafood experience that the entire family will enjoy. We are a hidden little secret to all of our locals and some of our Winter Residents too.
We have a full service bar and we hear from our customers that our Margaritas are the best ever! Here at Gary's, we have made a lot of friends and we are sure that after coming in, you will be one as well.
Our staff is friendly and fun and want you to have a good time while you're here. Come kick back and discover what casual Florida dining is all about. We are sure you will not forget your visit to Gary's. We are centrally located between Orlando and Tampa off of Hwy 27 and easy access from I-4.
Food so good you’ll Slap Yo Momma. There are places that have Sea Food on the Menu and then There’s G.O.B. Where the Menu is on Sea Food. Prices are the Real Deal here as no Ocean Front means Gary doesn’t have to put on a front , less overhead means he’s got $$$ to spend on your Belly and we all know the Value in that. Friendly Staff and Staff Friendly and I wouldn’t Shuk u on that. We came across this by Happenstance and boy were we glad we did. Thanks Jack we will be Back. B-Man
—
R. Brian Roger
